{"tid":611521,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"除左藍領工，香港有咩工唔飽和?","createTime":"2018-03-31T05:55:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-05T12:10:18.000Z","uid":136252,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"a964e19ee6c9a2b22ab879aa6f9167b87a6dba72","tid":611521,"uid":136252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T05:55:50.000Z","msg":"利申先，學生，冇咩社會經驗<br />\n<br />\n我覺得好多勞力工都唔夠人，但仲係出好低人工請人。而叫做好少少既工就話飽和，成日炒人"},{"pid":"3856a4e3f9d9bb83e66fc7781c0c78de7dbd26cb","tid":611521,"uid":32250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T08:55:21.000Z","msg":"無"},{"pid":"f26881653e1cb102fdf4e844fc5ffa7d1efe7133","tid":611521,"uid":155949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3856a4e3f9d9bb83e66fc7781c0c78de7dbd26cb","tid":611521,"uid":32250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T08:55:21.000Z","msg":"無"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T12:33:05.000Z","msg":"Teller<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b456abfe75f38dd17d80c44f8dc31986d00b0448","tid":611521,"uid":136252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T13:53:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"625942d2698f321a65c978b35ef1f2e3114cd3de","tid":611521,"uid":55445,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T14:06:48.000Z","msg":"醫生"},{"pid":"f9812cf395073d737c0050c7da66d7b96b66cd8f","tid":611521,"uid":134834,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T14:24:06.000Z","msg":"睇樓主都係覺得所謂「好」少少既工都白領歎冷氣果d工<br />\n不過個現實你無專業資格既「好」工都係廢工易被取代既<br />\n所以個人工先會keep住低<br />\n藍領辛苦工好多都係專業野<br />\n姑勿論佢個行業前景係如何，但有技術性質就一定唔易取代<br />\n如果樓主執拗於「好唔好做」既問題上面，<br />\n咁我都可以好肯定話你聽，好做又高人工係講際遇，<br />\n十居其九都係好做就低人工，唔好做多數高人工，睇你點取捨，<br />\n希望樓主行少d冤枉路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"147d2b0d62ab9035eb765a91e0c1a98c0b1e77ea","tid":611521,"uid":32250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f26881653e1cb102fdf4e844fc5ffa7d1efe7133","tid":611521,"uid":155949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3856a4e3f9d9bb83e66fc7781c0c78de7dbd26cb","tid":611521,"uid":32250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T08:55:21.000Z","msg":"無"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T12:33:05.000Z","msg":"Teller<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T14:59:23.000Z","msg":"Teller <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b07403fe699387c338e8359fc449570f5f345dfb","tid":611521,"uid":25221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T10:35:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"53f7760a82d771e966ca5071750bad81daf6c9b2","tid":611521,"uid":32250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b07403fe699387c338e8359fc449570f5f345dfb","tid":611521,"uid":25221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"147d2b0d62ab9035eb765a91e0c1a98c0b1e77ea","tid":611521,"uid":32250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f26881653e1cb102fdf4e844fc5ffa7d1efe7133","tid":611521,"uid":155949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T12:33:05.000Z","msg":"Teller<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=